The app sets no HTTP security headers. Responses are missing `X-Content-Type-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, `X-Frame-Options`, `Content-Security-Policy`, and more. This leaves the app vulnerable to clickjacking, MIME sniffing, and other browser-based attacks.

**Recommendation:** Use `helmet`:
