| # | Issue | OWASP | Severity | Effort |
|---|-------|-------|----------|--------|
| 1 | No body parser / input validation | A03 | 🔴 Critical | Low |
| 2 | No security headers | A05 | 🔴 Critical | Low |
| 3 | PII exposed without auth | A01/A02 | 🔴 Critical | Medium |
| 4 | No rate limiting | A04 | 🟠 High | Low |
| 5 | No CORS policy | A05 | 🟠 High | Low |
| 6 | Hardcoded configuration | A05 | 🟠 High | Low |
| 7 | No error handling | A09 | 🟡 Medium | Low |
| 8 | No request logging | A09 | 🟡 Medium | Low |
| 9 | No dependency management | A06 | 🟡 Medium | Low |
| 10 | console.log in production | — | 🟢 Info | Low |

